{
  "stem": "24884.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was 1940 or '41, when you had to start wearing the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even then, some people didn't sew it on the coat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They put it on with a certain way, that you could take it off and put it on, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and tried to, you know, go a little bit against the law.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did that too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "90% of the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only when I wanted to sneak into a movie or meet my friends at a certain place where we were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or we wore our handbag like this, that you didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I really don't remember everything about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because this is somehow that you-- that you don't want to keep that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't want to think about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you mean if we light-- lit candles on Friday?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother did not do that, because she felt she's alone and there's no husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Except that in the home where I was, we did it all the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the house by my aunt and uncle, we did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She knew it was a holiday, and she went to occasionally to a temple on the high holy days, but that was about it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I would say that 80% of my friends got killed in the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other 20% immigrated [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to Israel, to South America, and to here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have friends still here, in the United States, in New York.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have one girl I'm very friendly with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still correspond with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's a Gentile girl, in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or was it '41, at the end of '41?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
